text: National Highway 143H, commonly referred to as NH 143H is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 43. NH-143H runs in the states of Odisha and Jharkhand in India. == Route == NH143H connects Joram, Ambapani, Salangabahal, Bihabandh and Litebeda in the states of Jharkhand and Odisha. == Junctions == : Terminal near Joram. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 143H on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Jharkhand Category:National Highways in Odisha
